      <title>摩根大通的 Michele 看好新兴市场债券和 CCC 债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/jpmorgan-s-michele-likes-emerging-market-debt-ccc-bonds-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通资产管理公司全球固定收益主管鲍勃·米歇尔 (Bob Michele) 表示，摩根大通继续看好信贷，且近期不会出现经济衰退。他在“彭博监控：美联储决定”节目中发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/jpmorgan-s-michele-likes-emerging-market-debt-ccc-bonds-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 19:08:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
