      <title>美联储自 2021 年以来首次调整关键 RRP 政策工具利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/fed-tweaks-rate-on-key-rrp-policy-tool-for-first-time-since-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储除了主要降息外，还降低了用于帮助控制基准利率的工具利率，以支持美国融资市场的平稳运行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/fed-tweaks-rate-on-key-rrp-policy-tool-for-first-time-since-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 19:03:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
